T00:11:16.000Z","msg":"民協唔係民煮派？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-12T00:13:24.000Z","msg":"佢地要塭野推<br />\n詳情睇出面啲post<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"682a67c9e2fa6a13e83a0df1a562fe5f3af3e0d0","tid":589390,"uid":63909,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"2c569917b76fd2a6c53fbaaf69291d39c15e1ce0","tid":589390,"uid":44358,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-12T00:12:29.000Z","msg":"駛 spin<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n焦土咁開心，依家你焦個狗閪瞬，開心啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-12T00:21:22.000Z","msg":"邊個做有咩開心唔開心<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我唔會信港共投票<br />\n但睇到有班友賴呢樣賴個様<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e11b46bcae779b2209525cb0525cd8b45c280dc6","tid":589390,"uid":61280,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-12T00:27:00.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\"><br />\n<br />\n「姚松炎今次做選舉工程，同我哋傳統政黨，真係好唔同，我哋唔係好慣，尤其係打開地面戰嗰班，其實一直覺得佢危。<br />\n<br />\n我哋擺街站、洗樓、去屋邨，佢哋認為唔使做好多呢啲，覺得做好網上，網上反應熱烈，就好有信心。<br />\n<br />\n即使佢哋助選團，或者幫忙嘅團體開（街）站，但好似用錯力，星期五、六下晝，喺佐敦開站，我哋一般唔會咁做，因為嗰啲係街客，去行街，唔係選民；即使開喺住宅區，有啲朝早9點後先至開，嗰啲時間，人人返晒工，開站都無咩用。<br />\n<br />\n姚松炎團隊去土瓜灣少數族裔拉票，好奇怪，或者踩單車，我哋好多人睇到，暈低咁滯。或者係我哋太傳統，唔慣咁做。<br />\n<br />\n不過泛民好多大佬，就好buy佢呢套，所以一直覺得九西呢個位好易贏，無咩危機感，其實我地做開地區嘅，睇佢唔係咁穩陣。<br />\n<br />\n佢哋呢種選舉工程，喺比例代表制，效果可能會比較好，今次補選只係選一個位，未必可以咁打選戰。今次投票率咁低，有好多原因，如果唔諗點樣做，下次補選，我擔心唔容易贏。」<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/03/12/082155_ea3dc39ca0b2f6b5f17abddec1f0e9a4.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F03%2F12%2F082155_ea3dc39ca0b2f6b5f17abddec1f0e9a4.png&h=65e18a89&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n</span></strong></span><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/03/12/082539_ea3dc39ca0b2f6b5f17abddec1f0e9a4.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F03%2F12%2F082539_ea3dc39ca0b2f6b5f17abddec1f0e9a4.png&h=e96c93c8&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"b1f56ed62365a7c86f7754d8e15a74be83cce9cf","tid":589390,"uid":63909,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"1d6dc317a42363f2a918e4fb52f50f5cbd92e0c1","tid":589390,"uid":141151,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"f75833e773d4fda2deda7658573500fbf840c414","tid":589390,"uid":63909,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-12T00:09:50.000Z","msg":"錯不在民煮派<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-03-12T00:11:16.000Z","msg":"民協唔係民煮派？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-12T00:35:53.000Z","msg":"咁佢地咪可以話唔撚團結囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"857133e6bb9182d47793a9af4f79232e7eb96474","tid":589390,"uid":63909,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"b1f56ed62365a7c86f7754d8e15a74be83cce9cf","tid":589390,"uid":63909,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"1d6dc317a42363f2a918e4fb52f50f5cbd92e0c1","tid":589390,"uid":141151,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"f75833e773d4fda2deda7658573500fbf840c414","tid":589390,"uid":63909,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-12T00:09:50.000Z","msg":"錯不在民煮派<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-03-12T00:11:16.000Z","msg":"民協唔係民煮派？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"20